\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta_{i+1}\left(x\right)=\theta_{i}\left(x\right)+\alpha\sum_{y\in nn(x)}\theta_{i}\left(y\right)+\frac{K}{2\pi}\sin\left(2\pi\theta_{i}\left(x\right)\right)
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $nn(x)$
\end_inset

 is the set of nearest neighbors of 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
